metadata.editComments:
Someone might want to notate the higher melody in the 2nd half of bar 8, but that person is not me.
I considered breaking this into 2 sections but I don't really think the first 8 stand strong enough on their own and the rest is pretty continuous. Plus, it's way easier to add sections that take them out.
